### HTTP Request

`GET https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/collection/COLLECTION_ID`

### Query Parameters

| Parameter        | Required   | Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|------------------|------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| shop_id          | true       | Your API key                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
| did              | true       | Device ID. You get it from `init` method in SDK.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
| sid              | true       | Temporary user session ID                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |



